org.apache.uima.collection.base_cpm.CasObjectProcessor, org.apache.uima.collection.base_cpm.CasProcessor, org.apache.uima.collection.CasConsumer, org.apache.uima.resource.ConfigurableResource, org.apache.uima.resource.Resource
public class AnnotationPrinter
extends org.apache.uima.collection.CasConsumer_ImplBase
implements org.apache.uima.collection.base_cpm.CasObjectProcessor

AnnotationPrinter prints to an output file all annotations in the CAS.
Parameters needed by the AnnotationPrinter are

  1. "outputFile" : file to which the output files should be written.

These parameters are set in the initialize method to the values specified in the descriptor file.
These may also be set by the application by using the setConfigParameterValue methods.

processCas

public void processCas(org.apache.uima.cas.CAS aCAS)
                throws org.apache.uima.resource.ResourceProcessException
Processes the CasContainer which was populated by the SimpleGeneAnnotator.
In this case, the CAS index is iterated over selected annotations, sorted according to annotation id and start fields and printed out into an output file.

指定者：
接口 org.apache.uima.collection.base_cpm.CasObjectProcessor 中的 processCas
参数：
aCAS - CasContainer which has been populated by the TAEs
